-- Australia's Assistant Treasurer Releases Draft Scrip Rollover Legislation
-- Gemma Daley
-- 2010-04-21T23:25:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-21/australia-s-assistant-treasurer-releases-draft-scrip-rollover-legislation.html

          
          
             Australia released draft
legislation to make it easier for some mergers and takeovers to
qualify for capital gains tax scrip for scrip rollover,
Assistant Treasurer Nick Sherry said in an e-mailed statement.   
          
          


  


        